# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:10
translate spanish reba10_4a2deb47:

    # "My phone starts buzzing. Reba is calling."
    "Mi teléfono empieza a vibrar. Es Reba llamando."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:14
translate spanish reba10_0783e6df:

    # rb "[pcname]! I need some help!"
    rb "¡[pcname]! ¡Necesito ayuda!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:15
translate spanish reba10_e73f463e:

    # pc "What happened? What's wrong?"
    pc "¿Qué ha pasado? ¿Qué pasa?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:16
translate spanish reba10_e9c8b26b:

    # rb "My idiot brother stole my truck!"
    rb "¡Mi hermano idiota me ha robado la camioneta!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:17
translate spanish reba10_3b4e773f:

    # rb "He wrecked his dang car then he asked me to borrow my truck and I tole him \"Heck no!\", but then he waited 'til I had to pee and while I was on the dang toilet, he grabbed my keys and took off in my dang truck!"
    rb "Ha destrozado su maldito coche y luego me pidió prestada mi camioneta y le dije «¡Ni hablar!», pero esperó a que tuviera que ir al baño y, mientras estaba en el maldito retrete, ¡me cogió las llaves y se largó con mi maldita camioneta!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:18
translate spanish reba10_2bc9e836:

    # rb "I know where he went though! Can you just come give me a ride out there?"
    rb "¡Pero sé adónde se ha ido! ¿Puedes venir a recogerme y llevarme hasta allí?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:19
translate spanish reba10_bc9a4692:

    # pc "Um, sure. Yeah, want me to pick you up at your trailer then?"
    pc "Eh, claro. Sí, ¿quieres que te recoja en tu caravana?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:20
translate spanish reba10_f108435a:

    # rb "Yeah! I'm outside waiting. I'm so mad, I'm going to knock the tar out of him."
    rb "¡Sí! Estoy fuera esperando. Estoy tan enfadada que le voy a dar una paliza."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:21
translate spanish reba10_58dabe1b:

    # pc "Okay, calm down. I'm on my way."
    pc "Vale, cálmate. Voy para allá."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:24
translate spanish reba10_314623f0:

    # "I start to drive out towards Reba's place, hoping that this isn't going to turn into a big confrontation."
    "Empiezo a conducir hacia la casa de Reba, esperando que esto no se convierta en una gran pelea."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:25
translate spanish reba10_e4690563:

    # "I care about Reba, but man I don't want to get involved in all that drama really."
    "Me preocupo por Reba, pero, tío, la verdad es que no quiero meterme en todo ese lío."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:28
translate spanish reba10_56e9e1ec:

    # "As soon as I get to her trailer, she runs up and jumps in the passenger seat."
    "En cuanto llego a su caravana, ella sale corriendo y se sube al asiento del copiloto."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:29
translate spanish reba10_f51bc837:

    # rb "Okay let's go."
    rb "Vale, vamos."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:30
translate spanish reba10_5c2f35ad:

    # rb "Out to the highway and take a right."
    rb "Sal a la autopista y gira a la derecha."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:31
translate spanish reba10_08551511:

    # pc "You got it."
    pc "Entendido."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:34
translate spanish reba10_e13860c9:

    # rb "I can't believe he's doing this. I told him I don't want to be involved in this junk."
    rb "No puedo creer que esté haciendo esto. Le dije que no quería meterme en este lío."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:35
translate spanish reba10_6e56d6c2:

    # pc "In what junk?"
    pc "¿En qué lío?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:36
translate spanish reba10_b814e868:

    # rb "He's out where he and his buddies make their drugs. I don't want my dang truck out there."
    rb "Está en el lugar donde él y sus amigos fabrican las drogas. No quiero que mi maldita camioneta esté por ahí."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:37
translate spanish reba10_c336c275:

    # pc "That's understandable."
    pc "Es comprensible."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:38
translate spanish reba10_4fffe399:

    # rb "I mean, he shouldn't be out there in the first place! But he keeps trying to pull me in too, and I don't want any part of it."
    rb "¡Es que, para empezar, ni siquiera debería estar ahí fuera! Pero sigue intentando meterme en líos, y yo no quiero tener nada que ver con eso."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:39
translate spanish reba10_dca0d099:

    # rb "I'm so dang mad. I'm going to wring his neck."
    rb "Estoy tan cabreada... Le voy a retorcer el cuello."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:40
translate spanish reba10_533f4947:

    # rb "Turn left up here at the 162 mile marker."
    rb "Gira a la izquierda aquí, en el kilómetro 162."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:42
translate spanish reba10_cbbf45b6:

    # pc "Is there going to be a problem here? Should we call the police?"
    pc "¿Va a haber algún problema aquí? ¿Deberíamos llamar a la policía?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:43
translate spanish reba10_8b8a99ed:

    # rb "Naw, we don't need to do that. Just get me there and I'll take care of my stupid brother."
    rb "No, no hace falta. Solo llévame hasta allí y yo me encargaré de mi estúpido hermano."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:44
translate spanish reba10_0e8d71e2:

    # pc "I don't want you to get hurt."
    pc "No quiero que te hagan daño."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:45
translate spanish reba10_421bc2bc:

    # rb "He wouldn't dare."
    rb "No se atrevería."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:46
translate spanish reba10_4add003d:

    # rb "Take that road there, the narrow, rocky one."
    rb "Toma esa carretera de ahí, la estrecha y rocosa."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:48
translate spanish reba10_f0f6025c:

    # "Just then, I realize that I've been here before. This is the same path I drove down when I delivered that package for Izzy."
    "En ese momento, me doy cuenta de que ya he estado aquí antes. Es el mismo camino por el que conduje cuando entregué ese paquete para Izzy."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:49
translate spanish reba10_9bb69c53:

    # "The one that led to the bunker out in the woods."
    "El que llevaba al búnker en el bosque."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:50
translate spanish reba10_85f255cd:

    # "Is Mickey involved with the same people?"
    "¿Está Mickey metido con la misma gente?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:54
translate spanish reba10_ccb00f9d:

    # "A few minutes later, I pull up in front of the bunker and my thoughts are confirmed."
    "Unos minutos más tarde, me detengo frente al búnker y mis sospechas se confirman."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:55
translate spanish reba10_04a16677:

    # rb "This is the place."
    rb "Este es el lugar."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:56
translate spanish reba10_1dd67079:

    # pc "This feels dangerous, Reba. Maybe we should just call the police."
    pc "Esto me da mala espina, Reba. Quizás deberíamos llamar a la policía."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:57
translate spanish reba10_fc1eaa08:

    # rb "They all know me here. It's fine. Just stay in the car, okay? Hopefully he left my keys in the truck and I can just take it and leave."
    rb "Aquí todos me conocen. No pasa nada. Quédate en el coche, ¿vale? Con suerte, habrá dejado mis llaves en la camioneta y podré cogerla y marcharme."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:60
translate spanish reba10_8008c40a:

    # "I watch as she goes over to her truck, opens the door and looks inside."
    "La veo acercarse a su camioneta, abrir la puerta y mirar dentro."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:62
translate spanish reba10_ebed6c35:

    # "There's no guards outside, unlike last time I was here."
    "No hay guardias fuera, a diferencia de la última vez que estuve aquí."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:63
translate spanish reba10_2d50ab1d:

    # "I keep glancing over towards the door to the bunker, hoping that it won't open, and we won't have to deal with her brother and his friends."
    "No dejo de mirar hacia la puerta del búnker, con la esperanza de que no se abra y no tengamos que lidiar con su hermano y sus amigos."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:64
translate spanish reba10_8559a5fe:

    # "But after a few moments, those hopes are dashed."
    "Pero al cabo de unos instantes, esas esperanzas se desvanecen."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:67
translate spanish reba10_252a1f14:

    # "Guard" "Hey, girl, what the hell are you doing here?"
    "Guard" "Oye, chica, ¿qué demonios haces aquí?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:68
translate spanish reba10_b44d866b:

    # rb "You better back off, Dave. I'm in no mood for you."
    rb "Más te vale apartarte, Dave. No estoy de humor para ti."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:69
translate spanish reba10_9cd788e9:

    # lee "Now come on, Reba. You shouldn't be out here."
    lee "Venga ya, Reba. No deberías estar aquí fuera."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:70
translate spanish reba10_581f53b2:

    # rb "I don't {i}want{/i} to be out here, but my stupid brother stole my dang truck! Tell him to come out here."
    rb "¡No {i}quiero{/i} estar aquí fuera, pero mi estúpido hermano me ha robado la maldita camioneta! Dile que salga aquí fuera."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:73
translate spanish reba10_1773de58:

    # rb "Mickey! Get your butt out here and give me my dang keys!"
    rb "¡Mickey! ¡Mueve el culo y ven aquí a darme mis malditas llaves!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:74
translate spanish reba10_55d7c87b:

    # lee "Reba, just calm down now."
    lee "Reba, cálmate ya."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:75
translate spanish reba10_af30b43d:

    # "Dave" "Yeah, baby, ain't no need for fightin'."
    "Dave" "Sí, nena, no hay por qué pelear."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:76
translate spanish reba10_1f64ecee:

    # rb "Don't you \"baby\" me! I ain't your dang baby!"
    rb "¡No me llames «nena»! ¡No soy tu maldita nena!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:77
translate spanish reba10_ec653d1e:

    # rb "{size=+20}MICKEY!!!!{/size}"
    rb "{size=+20}¡MICKEY!!!!{/size}"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:80
translate spanish reba10_c2ec983f:

    # "At that, he comes bursting out of the bunkers door and walks towards her."
    "Al oír eso, sale disparado por la puerta del búnker y camina hacia ella."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:81
translate spanish reba10_a080820d:

    # mk "What the fuck, sis?"
    mk "¿Qué coño pasa, hermana?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:82
translate spanish reba10_1abda826:

    # mk "Why are you out here?"
    mk "¿Por qué estás aquí fuera?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:83
translate spanish reba10_3d7aa408:

    # rb "Cause you stole my dang truck, you moron!"
    rb "¡Porque me has robado mi maldita camioneta, idiota!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:84
translate spanish reba10_aa828ca0:

    # rb "Give me my keys!"
    rb "¡Dame mis llaves!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:85
translate spanish reba10_4bfedf50:

    # mk "Did you bring that city slicker boyfriend with you? You brought him out here?"
    mk "¿Te has traído a ese novio urbanita contigo? ¿Lo has traído aquí?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:86
translate spanish reba10_3e5c44aa:

    # mk "Now why the fuck would you do that, Reba? You need a whuppin'?"
    mk "¿Por qué coño harías eso, Reba? ¿Necesitas una paliza?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:87
translate spanish reba10_c12128df:

    # "At that, I open the door and step out. They can argue all they want, but I'm not going to sit in the car while he threatens to hurt her."
    "En ese momento, abro la puerta y salgo. Pueden discutir todo lo que quieran, pero no me voy a quedar sentado en el coche mientras él amenaza con hacerle daño."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:90
translate spanish reba10_9bbc3d4b:

    # rb "It's fine, [pcname]. Get back in the car."
    rb "No pasa nada, [pcname]. Vuelve al coche."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:91
translate spanish reba10_c6d04a1c:

    # mk "Yeah, get back in the car, bitch!"
    mk "¡Sí, vuelve al coche, zorra!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:92
translate spanish reba10_0aa316da:

    # rb "Just give me my truck keys and we'll leave, Mickey."
    rb "Dame las llaves de mi camioneta y nos iremos, Mickey."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:93
translate spanish reba10_d616ee46:

    # mk "You shouldn't have brought him out here, Reba! You know that!"
    mk "¡No deberías haberlo traído aquí, Reba! ¡Lo sabes!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:94
translate spanish reba10_dfb1dc33:

    # rb "You shouldn't have stolen my truck!"
    rb "¡No deberías haber robado mi camioneta!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:98
translate spanish reba10_f461d1bd:

    # "Then Mickey has a pistol in his hand, pulled from the back of his pants, pointed directly at my chest."
    "Entonces Mickey saca una pistola de la parte trasera de sus pantalones y me apunta directamente al pecho."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:99
translate spanish reba10_4bf3ee55:

    # "My breath catches in my throat and my heart practically stops beating."
    "Se me corta la respiración y mi corazón prácticamente deja de latir."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:100
translate spanish reba10_82d32150:

    # mk "You want me to kill him, Reba? That what you want?"
    mk "¿Quieres que lo mate, Reba? ¿Es eso lo que quieres?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:101
translate spanish reba10_52cc6548:

    # mk "He can't know about this place!"
    mk "¡No puede enterarse de este lugar!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:102
translate spanish reba10_12b1b868:

    # rb "Mickey you better put that dang gun away!"
    rb "¡Mickey, más te vale guardar esa maldita pistola!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:103
translate spanish reba10_4c8c649e:

    # rb "You hurt him and I'll tell everybody about this place. I'll tell the whole dang city about the drugs you make out here."
    rb "Si le haces daño, se lo contaré a todo el mundo. Le diré a toda la maldita ciudad lo de las drogas que fabricáis aquí."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:104
translate spanish reba10_82647901:

    # mk "You better shut your fucking mouth."
    mk "Más te vale cerrar esa puta boca."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:105
translate spanish reba10_872b6b4e:

    # rb "You gonna shoot me too?"
    rb "¿También me vas a disparar a mí?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:106
translate spanish reba10_483d1f88:

    # mk "You know I ain't gonna hurt you."
    mk "Sabes que no te voy a hacer daño."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:109
translate spanish reba10_19094ad9:

    # "She pushes him backwards, her eyes lighting up with a fire that I hadn't seen before."
    "Ella lo empuja hacia atrás, con los ojos encendidos por un fuego que no le había visto antes."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:110
translate spanish reba10_33ae7cdf:

    # rb "Then put the fucking gun away and give me my fucking keys!"
    rb "¡Pues guarda esa puta pistola y dame mis putas llaves!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:113
translate spanish reba10_b1cbd54e:

    # "He pulls a keychain out of his pocket and tosses it at her."
    "Él saca un llavero del bolsillo y se lo lanza."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:114
translate spanish reba10_4c2f2b0d:

    # mk "Just take it and get the fuck out!"
    mk "¡Cógelas y lárgate de aquí!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:117
translate spanish reba10_eea82588:

    # "With that, he turns and walks back towards the door of the bunker, while she looks at me."
    "Dicho esto, se da la vuelta y camina de vuelta hacia la puerta del búnker, mientras ella me mira."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:118
translate spanish reba10_3b376fe5:

    # rb "Go ahead and get back in the car and head out. I'll follow you."
    rb "Vete, vuelve al coche y lárgate. Yo te seguiré."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:119
translate spanish reba10_1199f80b:

    # pc "Yeah, okay."
    pc "Sí, vale."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:122
translate spanish reba10_f8803503:

    # "I do as she said and get back into my car, turn it around and start driving away."
    "Hago lo que me dice y vuelvo a mi coche, doy la vuelta y empiezo a alejarme."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:123
translate spanish reba10_80782ff7:

    # "I'm still shaking a bit from having that gun pointed at me, and worried that those guys will change their minds and come back out after us."
    "Todavía tiemblo un poco por haber tenido esa pistola apuntándome, y me preocupa que esos tipos cambien de opinión y salgan a por nosotros."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:124
translate spanish reba10_99981def:

    # "Maybe they wouldn't have hurt Reba, but I felt like I was one wrong move away from getting shot there."
    "Quizá no le habrían hecho daño a Reba, pero sentí que un solo movimiento en falso y me habrían disparado allí mismo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:125
translate spanish reba10_0c5c5487:

    # "I try to focus on breathing and cooling off while I make the drive back to her trailer."
    "Intento concentrarme en respirar y calmarme mientras conduzco de vuelta a su caravana."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:128
translate spanish reba10_ea19fc19:

    # "When we get there and park, she gets out of her truck and rushes over to where I'm standing, next to my car."
    "Cuando llegamos y aparcamos, ella sale de su camioneta y corre hacia donde estoy, junto a mi coche."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:129
translate spanish reba10_9ba5be79:

    # rb "I'm so sorry about that. I shouldn't have brought you into this."
    rb "Lo siento mucho. No debería haberte metido en esto."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:130
translate spanish reba10_06e8ff4f:

    # pc "Was he really going to shoot me?"
    pc "¿De verdad iba a dispararme?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:131
translate spanish reba10_5001010d:

    # rb "I don't think so. He's just puffing up his chest in front of his stupid friends."
    rb "No lo creo. Solo está alardeando delante de sus estúpidos amigos."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:132
translate spanish reba10_5f2782fc:

    # rb "It's probably better if you don't come around here for a while though."
    rb "Aunque probablemente sea mejor que no vengas por aquí durante un tiempo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:133
translate spanish reba10_a5ae1027:

    # rb "God, I hate this so much."
    rb "Dios, odio esto tanto."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:136
translate spanish reba10_9da8caac:

    # "She collapses against my shoulder, crying, her tears soaking into my shirt."
    "Se derrumba contra mi hombro, llorando, con sus lágrimas empapándome la camisa."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:137
translate spanish reba10_71986c9f:

    # rb "I'm sorry!"
    rb "¡Lo siento!"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:138
translate spanish reba10_9ca48230:

    # rb "I don't know what to do. This whole situation just sucks so bad."
    rb "No sé qué hacer. Toda esta situación es un asco."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:139
translate spanish reba10_22d1800a:

    # rb "I feel so trapped."
    rb "Me siento tan atrapada."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:142
translate spanish reba10_524d8557:

    # rb "I know. Thank you, [pcname]."
    rb "Lo sé. Gracias, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:143
translate spanish reba10_11a36825:

    # rb "It makes me feel a little better to have somebody who I can count on, at least."
    rb "Me hace sentir un poco mejor tener a alguien con quien pueda contar, al menos."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:145
translate spanish reba10_e221217d:

    # rb "I can't."
    rb "No puedo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:146
translate spanish reba10_381604a1:

    # rb "Thank you for offering."
    rb "Gracias por ofrecerte."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:147
translate spanish reba10_3873e0a1:

    # rb "But I just can't leave Mama."
    rb "Pero no puedo dejar a mamá."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:150
translate spanish reba10_3a44c154:

    # "She lifts her head up and kisses me."
    "Levanta la cabeza y me besa."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:151
translate spanish reba10_72565e2e:

    # rb "Thank you, [pcname]."
    rb "Gracias, [pcname]."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:152
translate spanish reba10_dc63d368:

    # rb "Thank you for coming when I call for help."
    rb "Gracias por venir cuando te pido ayuda."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:153
translate spanish reba10_a248948f:

    # pc "Of course."
    pc "Por supuesto."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:154
translate spanish reba10_ab6186a8:

    # "She kisses me deeply, like she never wants to let go."
    "Me besa profundamente, como si nunca quisiera soltarme."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:155
translate spanish reba10_4e13f906:

    # "I just want to pick her up and carry her away from here. To protect her from her brother. To give her a different life."
    "Solo quiero cogerla en brazos y llevármela lejos de aquí. Para protegerla de su hermano. Para darle una vida diferente."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:158
translate spanish reba10_4dcc5b12:

    # rb "That was new. With the tongues and stuff."
    rb "Eso era nuevo. Lo de las lenguas y todo eso."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:159
translate spanish reba10_4c2fa35d:

    # pc "Yeah, it was nice."
    pc "Sí, estuvo bien."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:160
translate spanish reba10_905d8d36:

    # rb "I'm sorry I'm such a mess."
    rb "Siento estar tan desorientada."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:161
translate spanish reba10_1156eece:

    # rb "I'll call you again soon, okay? Hopefully under better circumstances."
    rb "Te volveré a llamar pronto, ¿vale? Con suerte, en mejores circunstancias."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:162
translate spanish reba10_fcfea3e9:

    # rb "I should get inside. I have to make dinner for Mama."
    rb "Debería entrar. Tengo que preparar la cena para mamá."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:163
translate spanish reba10_778a0d21:

    # pc "Are you sure you're okay here?"
    pc "¿Seguro que estás bien aquí?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:164
translate spanish reba10_cac3bad5:

    # rb "Yeah. I'm okay. You should go though."
    rb "Sí. Estoy bien. Pero deberías irte."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:165
translate spanish reba10_a1f9a9c8:

    # pc "Okay. We'll talk again soon though, right?"
    pc "Vale. Hablaremos pronto, ¿verdad?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:166
translate spanish reba10_2013b004:

    # rb "For sure."
    rb "Claro."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:167
translate spanish reba10_f60181f8:

    # rb "Bye, [pcname]. Take care."
    rb "Adiós, [pcname]. Cuídate."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:168
translate spanish reba10_a5e10844:

    # pc "You too, Reba."
    pc "Tú también, Reba."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:171
translate spanish reba10_75f9ec13:

    # "I drive away, feeling bad for leaving her, trying to think of some way that I could help her."
    "Me alejo conduciendo, sintiéndome mal por dejarla, intentando pensar en alguna forma de ayudarla."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:172
translate spanish reba10_7c59bd27:

    # "The thing that keeps coming to mind is that bunker. Maybe I should go to the police about it?"
    "Lo único que no se me va de la cabeza es ese búnker. ¿Quizás debería acudir a la policía?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:173
translate spanish reba10_fde914b4:

    # "I worry about it getting Reba into more trouble, or that Mickey might come after me..."
    "Me preocupa que eso meta a Reba en más problemas, o que Mickey venga a por mí..."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:174
translate spanish reba10_df79fca0:

    # "But maybe telling the police is the right thing to do."
    "Pero quizás contárselo a la policía sea lo correcto."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:176
translate spanish reba10_92d394d0:

    # "Maybe I should talk to Jez about it? She might be able to help, and I know that this would help her with her case."
    "¿Quizás debería hablar con Jez sobre ello? Ella podría ayudarme, y sé que esto le serviría para su caso."

# game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:177
translate spanish reba10_f11fd044:

    # "I toss the idea back and forth in my mind the entire drive back towards town."
    "Le doy vueltas a la idea en mi cabeza durante todo el trayecto de vuelta a la ciudad."

translate spanish strings:

    # game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:2
    old "Go on a couple of dates with Reba."
    new "Queda un par de veces con Reba."

    # game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:3
    old "Then she will call you in the evening, needing your help."
    new "Luego te llamará por la noche, necesitando tu ayuda."

    # game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:141
    old "I'm sorry, I'm here for you"
    new "Lo siento, estoy aquí para ayudarte."

    # game/Scenes/Reba/reba10.rpy:144
    old "You could come stay with me for a while"
    new "Podrías venir a quedarte conmigo un tiempo."

